com.trogdadr2tr.GUI

Class ViewSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.trogdadr2tr.GUI.ViewSelector

  • public class ViewSelector
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the View Selections which are not implemented yet. Also contains the save and quit options. Text can be entered into the field and the save button can be pressed to submit the map.
    Author:
    Nick Schmidt
